        <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 30px auto 0 auto; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #4a5568; text-align: center; color: #a0aec0;">
            <p>© 2026 Fatimah Financial Hub. All calculators are for educational purposes.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
